                                p.lead.mp-1(style="padding-top:2rem") In late 2020 Apollo made the plunge into 3d through photogrammetry. First hundreds of pictures from every conceivable angle were taken with a cell phone. Those images were processed with AliceVision framework to scan the object into 3D data. The rough generated model was then cleaned up, optimized and rigged for animation in blender. 
                                p.lead.mp-1 Digitalization isn't always a difficult process, boxed food and products can easily be digitized with a few measurements and some prepared photos. 
